                                                        <div class="front-policy-item__title">
                                                            Third-party Cookies
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="front-policy-item__content">

                                                        <p>
                                                            Some cookies may be set by third-party payment providers, analytical platforms, security services, KYC/AML providers, and other counterparties and partners of the Group. Data exchange with third parties is regulated by applicable laws and mechanisms for
                                                            the international transfer of personal data in compliance with the key principles of Standard Contractual Clauses (SCCs).
                                                        </p>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>

                                            <div class="front-policy-item-wrapper">
