                                                                <div class="system-message__content">
                                                                    <div class="system-message__text">
                                                                        OORA3 Group of Companies complies with transparency and fair processing requirements by strictly minimizing the amount of personal data processed via cookies, utilizing data pseudonymization, tracking control tools, and data encryption during transmission
                                                                        and storage, as well as entering into high-quality SLA/DSA contracts with third-party service providers that include necessary requirements for the deletion and secure transfer of
